  50,27,"A d yini umsaĂąef is: \"a Mass nne$! Ur t rri$ d amjuĂŽ, d neppa i illan di ttelfan u$miq"
  50,28,"Inna: \"ur ppemnamaret ara $uĂŽI, imi wen d Zzewre$ aĂąggen"
  50,29,"Ur ipbeddil $uĂŽI wawal. Nek, ur ĂĂźuĂŽĂŽu$ imdanen"
  50,30,"Ass ideg ara Nini i Loahennama: \"ma teĂ§Ă§uĂŽev\"? A d tini: \"ma tella tmerna"
  50,31,"TqeĂŽb ed Loennet, ar wid ipĂȘezziben, ur tebĂąad"
  50,32,D tagi i wen ippuwaĂąĂąden; i yal atubi iĂȘerzen
