  57,1,"SbuccuĂąen, s ccekĂŽan Ăebbi, ayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n Ă»Ă»wab"
  57,2,"IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan; Issidir, Ineqq; u Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  57,3,"D Neppa ay d amezwaru, ay d aneggaru; d ayen d ibanen akked wayen iffren. Neppa IĂ©ĂŽa yal cci"
  57,4,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Sinna, IĂąannec af usgeld. IĂ©ĂŽa i ikeĂ§Ă§men ar tmurt, akked wayen id iteff$en segs, ayen id ippadren seg igenni, akked wayen ippalin $uĂŽes. Neppa yidwen, anda ma tellam. Ăebbi Ipwali ayen txedmem"
  57,5,IneS tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Ar Ăebbi ara u$alen lumuĂŽ
  57,6,"Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. IĂ©ĂŽa ayen illan deg idmaren"
  57,7,"Amnet s Ăebbi akked Umazan iS! Efket seg wayen i$ef i kwen Irra, degs, d igensas. Wid iumnen segwen, iseddqen, d ameqwĂŽan warraz nnsen"
  57,8,"Acu ikwen iu$en, ur tuminem ara s Ăebbi? Amazan ipnabi kwen a ppamnem s Mass nnwen. Ni$ $uĂŽes nnesba nnwen, ma tellam d lmumnin"
  57,9,"D Neppa id Issadren i umdan iS, issekniyen iberrzen, iwakken a kwen Issuffe$ si tillas ar tafat. Ih, Ăebbi, fellawen, d UmĂąin IpĂȘunun"
  57,10,"Acu ikwen iu$en, ur tepseddiqem deg ubrid n Ăebbi? N Ăebbi lweĂŽt n tmurt akked igenwan. Ur taĂądilem ara: wid iseddqen uqbel l$elb, u nnu$en, widak, ad aĂąlayen, nezzeh, sennig wid iseddqen sin $er da, u nnu$en. IwaĂąĂąed asen akw Ăebbi Ă»Ă»am. Ăebbi IĂ©ĂŽa ayen txedmem"
  57,11,"Win iĂŽevlen i Ăebbi aĂŽeĂźĂźal umĂąin, ad as d Irr s lufa, u ines warraz ukyis"
  57,12,"Asmi ara twaliv lmumnin, argaz tameĂźĂźut, teddun tafat nnsen zdat sen, u yeffus nnsen: \"a lxiĂŽ nnwen, assa, di leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen a pwekkĂŽem! D wagi ay d rrbeĂȘ ameqwĂŽaĂȘan"
  57,13,"Ass ideg ixabiten, argaz tameĂźĂźut, ad inin i wid iumnen: \"arout a$, a neddem si tafat nnwen\"! A d inin: \"u$alet ar deffir, a d tqelbem tafat\"! Ad yili garasen lĂȘiv, s tebburt. Zdaxel d aĂȘunu, beĂŽĂŽa, zdat es: aĂąaqeb"
  57,14,"Ad sen d siwlen: \"day ur nella ara yidwen\"? Ad inin: \"ih! Maca, thewwlem iman nnwen, tekkukram, tcukkem, $elvent kwen lemcihwat, armi d iusa lameĂŽ n Ăebbi. I$elv ikwen af Ăebbi, u$ellav"
  57,15,"Assa, ur ipwaĂźĂźaf feddu segwen, ne$ seg wid ijehlen. Axxam nnwen d times; d neppat ay d bab nnwen. A tu$alin tucmip"
  57,16,"Ăani maĂ§Ă§i d lawan, i wid iumnen, ad rgagin wulawen nnsen ar usmekti n Ăebbi, akked wayen id Issers n tidep? Ur ppilin am wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, zik, u tvul fellasen lmudda. D$a qquĂŽen wulawen nnsen; aĂźas degsen d iballa$en"
  57,17,"Ecfut ar Ăebbi Issidir tamurt, deffir tmeppant is. Ni$ Nbeggen awen d issekniyen, amendeĂŽ ma a pfehmem"
  57,18,"Ih, wid akked tid ipseddiqen, iĂŽeĂźlen i Ăebbi aĂŽeĂźĂźal umĂąin, ad asen d Irr s lufa, u nnsen arraz ukyis"
  57,19,"Wid iumnen s Ăebbi akked imazanen iS, d nitni ay d iĂȘeqqiyen, u d inagan ar Mass nnsen. Ad awin arraz nnsen akked tafat nnsen. Wid ijehlen u skaddben issekniyen nneÂŁ, widak d at ujajiĂȘ"
  57,20,"Cfut ar tameddurt n ddunit d urar kan, d zzhu, d acebbeĂȘ, d zzux garawen, asuget n wayla akked derya. Am umedya ugeffur. Im$an is Ăąaoben ijehliyen; sinna, ad isliwen, a ten twaliv ppiwĂŽi$en; d$a ad ĂȘevmen. Di laxeĂŽt, aĂąaqeb uqsiĂȘ akked ssmaĂȘ s$uĂŽ Ăebbi, akked llza. Tameddurt n ddunit d zzehwa kan ip$uĂŽĂŽun"
  57,21,"ÂŁiwlet ar ssmaĂȘ n Mass nnwen, akked Loennet iwesĂąan am tmurt akked igenni, teppuhegga d i wid iumnen s Ăebbi akked imazanen iS. D wagi ay d lfevl n Ăebbi. Ippak it i win i S ihwan. Ăebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwĂŽaĂȘan"
