  62,2,"D Neppa id Iuznen i wid ur ne$ĂŽi, Amazan segsen, iqqaĂŽ asen issekniyen iS. Izizdig iten, isselmad asen Tazmamt akked Ă»Ă»wab, xas llan, zik, di ttelfan n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  62,3,"U i wid nniven, mara awven $uĂŽsen. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n Ă»Ă»wab"
  62,4,"D wagi ay d lfevl n Ăebbi. Ippak it i win Ib$a. Ăebbi, d bab n lfevl ameqwĂŽahan"
  62,5,"Am wid iwumi ippukelfen s TuĂŽa, ur p ssawven. Cuban a$yul ibubben tizmamin. I icmet umedya n ugdud inekĂŽen issekniyen n Ăebbi! Ăebbi ur Inehhu ara agdud imednas"
  62,6,"Ini: \"a yudayen, ma t$ilem d kunwi ay d iĂȘbiben n Ăebbi, war imdanen, ssutret tameppant, ma tessawalem tidep"
  62,7,"Ur p ssuturen ara, d awez$i, ilmend igiten nnsen. Ăebbi Issen imednas"
  62,8,"Ini: \"tameppant iwumi tregwlem, a kwen id temmager, war ccekk. Sinna, a kwen awin ar Win IĂ©ĂŽan ayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. Ad awen Imel ayen txeddmem"
  62,9,"A wid iumnen! Ma ssawlen d i tĂ©allit, ass unejmuĂą, $iwlet ar usmekti n Ăebbi, ĂȘebset ttjaĂŽa. Ppif akka i kunwi, lemmer tessinem"
  62,10,"Mi tfukk tĂ©allit, mfaĂŽaqet di tmurt, nadit lfevl n Ăebbi, mmektit ed aĂźas Ăebbi, amar a prebĂȘem"
  62,11,"Mi walan ssuq, ne$ anecĂŽeĂȘ, ad azlen $uĂŽes, a k ooen tbeddev. Ini: \"ayen illan ar Ăebbi yif anecĂŽeĂȘ akked ssuq. Ăebbi Yif akw iĂŽeĂ©Ă©aqen"
  63,1,"Ma usan d $uĂŽek ixabiten, ad ak inin: \"a ncehhed ar keĂ§Ă§, war ccekk, d Amazan n Ăebbi\". Ăebbi IĂ©ĂŽa ar keĂ§Ă§, war ccekk, d Amazan iS. Ăebbi ad Icehhed ar, s tidep, ixabiten d ikeddaben"
  63,2,"Ăesben tagallit nnsen d laĂąnaya, d$a ssefĂŽa$en abrid n Ăebbi. Ihi, a yicmet wayen xeddmen"
  63,3,"Akka, acku llan umnen, sinna, jehlen. Ppusel$en wulawen nnsen, d$a nitni ur mĂȘiĂ»en"
  63,4,"Mi ten twalav, a k taĂąoeb tiddi nnsen. Ma mmeslayen, tessemĂȘasev i wawal nnsen. Amzun nitni d is$aĂŽen i isenden, $ilen yal ti$ĂŽi fellasen. Acengu, d nitni; ĂȘader iman ik segsen. A ten Ine$ Ăebbi! AcĂȘal wexxĂŽen"
  63,5,"Ma nnan asen: \"yyaw, ad issuter Umazan n Ăebbi a ppeppusemmĂȘem\", ad bernen iqweĂŽĂŽa nnsen, a ten twaliv wexxĂŽen s tem$weĂŽ"
  63,6,"IĂąuva fellasen tessutrev, ne$ ur tessutrev ad ppusemmĂȘen. Ur sen IpsemmiĂȘ Ăebbi, d awez$i. Ăebbi, s tidep, ur Inehhu agdud iballa$en"
  63,7,"Nitni i iqqaĂŽen: \"ur pseddiqet, i wid iddan akked Umazan n Ăebbi, alamma mmebruzzĂąen\". N Ăebbi igerrujen igenwan akked tmurt, maca ixabiten ur mĂȘiĂ»en"
  63,8,"QqaĂŽen: \"ma nu$al ar Lmadina, war ccekk, uzmir ad issuffe$, segs, uĂŽhif\". Tazmert, n Ăebbi akked Umazan iS, akked lmumnin, maca, ixabiten ur Ă©ĂŽin"
  63,9,"A wid iumnen! ÂŁuĂŽwat a kwen ssbaĂąden, af usmekti n Ăebbi, wayla nnwen akked tarwa nnwen! Wid igan akka, ihi, widak d imexsuĂŽen"
  63,10,"Ssedqet seg wayen i wen Nefka, uqbel a d tas tmeppant ar yiwen degwen, ad yini: \"a Mass iw! Lemmer ad iyi TeswexxĂŽev ar lajel aqĂŽib, ad seddqe$, ad ili$ seg wid imaĂąnen"
  63,11,"Ur Irennu Ăebbi di laĂąmeĂŽ, d awez$i, ma iusa d lajel is. Ăebbi IppuxebbeĂŽ $ef wayen txeddmem"
  64,1,"I illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, sbuccuĂąen Ăebbi. IneS tagelda; ineS wannuz; Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  64,2,"Neppa ikwen Ixelqen; segwen ajehli, segwen lmumen. Ăebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem"
  64,3,"Ixleq tamurt akked igenwan, s tidep. Imsel ikwen, IĂ»eggem amsal nnwen. ÂŁuĂŽeS tu$alin"
  64,4,IĂ©ĂŽa i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. IĂ©ĂŽa ayen teffrem akked wayen tennam. Ăebbi IĂ©ĂŽa i illan deg idmaren
  64,5,"Ma iusa kwen id usali n wid illan, zik, d ijehliyen? JeĂŽben lwexda n tikli nnsen. Fellasen, aĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan"
  64,6,"Ayagi, imi sen ppasen imazanen nnsen s ubeggen. Nnan: \"aĂąni d amdan ara $ inhun\"? D$a jehlen, xedĂąan. Ur IclaĂą Ăebbi. Ăebbi d AsĂąay, d AmaĂązuz"
  64,7,"Pputebten ijehliyen ar, d awez$i, ur d pnekkaren. Ini: \"xaĂźi! S Mass iw, ard a d tekkrem, sinna ard a ppepwaxebbĂŽem $ef wayen txeddmem\"! Ayagi, i Ăebbi, d ushil"
  64,8,"Ihi, amnet s Ăebbi akked Umazan iS, akked tafat id Nessers. Ăebbi IppuxebbeĂŽ $ef wayen txeddmem"
  64,9,"Ass ideg ara kwen Issemlil, i wass ujemmel, ass nni, d ass um$uĂŽĂŽu. Win iumnen s Ăebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad as Ikkes tucmitin is, a t Issekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad iwekkeĂŽ i lebda. D wagi ay d rrbeĂȘ ameqwĂŽaĂȘan"
  64,10,"Wid ijehlen u inekĂŽen issekniyen nneÂŁ, widak d at tmes, degs ad wekkĂŽen. A taggara icemten"
  64,11,"Ur d teppas twa$it, siwa ma Irad Ăebbi. Win iumnen s Ăebbi, ad Inhu ul is. Ăebbi IĂ©ĂŽa yal cci"
  64,12,"A$et awal i Ăebbi, a$et awal i Umazan! Ma twexxĂŽem, i iwatan kan, i Umazan nneÂŁ, siwa anabi ipbegginen"
  64,13,"Ăebbi, ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Neppa. ÂŁef Ăebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin"
  64,14,"A wid iumnen! S tidep, kra n tlawin nnwen akked tarwa nnwen, d icenga nnwen. Ăadret iman nnwen segsen! Ma tsemmĂȘem, teppum, tsemmĂȘem, Ăebbi, s tidep, IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  64,15,"Ayla nnwen akked dderya nnwen, d ahewwel kan, wanag, ar Ăebbi, illa warraz ameqwĂŽahan"
  64,16,"Ăezzbet i Ăebbi ayen iwumi tzemrem. Ăesset, ĂŽavit, seddqet! Yif it i iman nnwen. Wid ikksen ccĂȘa i iman nnsen, widak d imerbaĂȘ"
  64,17,"Ma tĂŽevlem i Ăebbi aĂŽeĂźĂźal igerzen, ad awen d Irr sin imuren, ad awen IsemmeĂȘ. Ăebbi Iceffu, IĂȘellem"
  64,18,"Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ivehĂŽen, Uzmir, Bab n Ă»Ă»wab"
  65,1,"A Nnbi! Mara tebrum i tlawin, brut asent mara tĂąaddi tallit n tarda nnsent. Ăesbet tallit. Ăezzbet i Ăebbi, Mass nnwen. Ur tent ssuffu$et si texxamin nnsent, ur d teff$ent, siwa ma, s tidep, ccvent. D tigi ay d tilisa n Ăebbi. Win izegren tilisa n Ăebbi, ni$ idens imanis. Ur teĂ©ĂŽiv ara, ahat Ăebbi a d Iazen lameĂŽ, ssyen $eĂŽ da"
  65,2,"Mi ssawvent lajel nnsent, ĂąacĂŽet pent s lewqama, ne$ mfaĂŽaqet yidsent, s lewqama. Awit ed sin inagan iĂȘeqqiyen segwen, a d cehhden zdat Ăebbi. Ataya wayen u$uĂŽ ppunedĂŽen, wid iumnen s Ăebbi akked wass aneggaru. Win ipĂȘezziben i Ăebbi, ad as Ildi tibbura"
  65,3,"a t I$it s wanda ur iĂȘtim. Win iĂźĂźfen di Ăebbi, a t IqennaĂą. Ih, Ăebbi IssĂąadday lameĂŽ iS. Ni$ Ăebbi Iwzen yal cci"
  65,4,"I tigad, n tlawin nnwen, i iuysen tarda, ma illa ccekk, tallit ugani nnsent: krav wagguren. Akken i tid ur nebdi tarda. Tid ibbwin tadist, tallit nnsent ar tinnufra nnsent. Win ipĂȘezziben i Ăebbi, s lameĂŽ iS, ad as Istiser"
  65,5,"D wagi ay d lameĂŽ n Ăebbi i wen d Issers. Win ipĂȘezziben i Ăebbi, ad as Ikkes tucmitin is, ad Issali arraz is"
  65,6,"Ad asent tefkem tanezdu$t anda tzed$em, akken tewĂąam. Ur tent ĂźĂźuĂŽĂŽut s tririt nnsent ar lĂȘeĂŽs. Ma llant s tadist, Ă»eĂŽĂŽfet fellasent, alamma d tinnufra nnsent. Ma ssuĂźvent tarwa nnwen, efket asent taqdiĂąt nnsent; mwafaqet s tiĂ©eĂź. Ma temnamarem, a ppessuĂźĂźev tmeĂźĂźut nniven"
  65,7,"Bu udrim ad iĂ»eĂŽĂŽef segs. Win ixuĂ» ĂŽĂŽeĂ©q ad iĂ»eĂŽĂŽef seg wayen i s Ifka Ăebbi. Ur Ipkellif Ăebbi taĂŽwiĂȘt, siwa ar ayen i s Ifka. Ăebbi ad Issuffe$ laĂątab ar tafat"
  65,8,AcĂȘal n temdinin i inuqmen lameĂŽ n Mass nnsent akked imazanen iS! NĂȘuseb itent leĂȘsab uqsiĂȘ. NĂąaqeb itent s uĂąaqeb issexven
  65,9,JeĂŽĂŽbent lwexda igiten nnsent. D lexsaĂŽa ay d iooa lameĂŽ nnsent
  65,10,Ăebbi Ihegga yasen aĂąaqeb uqsiĂȘ. Ăezzbet i Ăebbi a yuĂąqilen iumnen! Ni$ Ăebbi Issers awen d asmekti
  65,11,"Amazan i wen immalen issekniyen n Ăebbi iberrzen, iwakken ad Issuffe$, si tillas ar tafat, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. Wid iumnen s Ăebbi, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Issekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkĂŽen i lebda. Ni$ Ăebbi Igerrez asen ĂŽĂŽeĂ©q"
  65,12,"Ăebbi i Ixelqen Ă»a igenwan, akked tmurt am nitni. LameĂŽ iprusu garasen, iwakken a ppeĂ©ĂŽem ar Ăebbi Izmer i yal cci, u Ăebbi Izzi i yal cci s tmusni"
  66,1,"A Nnbi! Ay$eĂŽ tgedlev ayen i k IĂȘell Ăebbi? TqennĂąav tilawin ik. Ăebbi IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  66,2,"Ăebbi IĂȘeppem fellawen a pĂȘentem. Ăebbi d Bab nnwen. Neppa d Amusnaw, d Bab n Ă»Ă»wab"
  66,3,"Mi inna Nnbi sser, i yiwet si tlawin is, u temla, Ăebbi Issken it i neppa. IxebbeĂŽ s wumur, iffer amur, segs. Mi p iaĂąlem s waya, tenna: \"wi k imlan aya\"? Inna: \"Imla yi t Win Issnen, IppuxebbĂŽen"
  66,4,"Ma tutubemt Ăebbi, ihi knan wulawen n kwent. Ma tedduklemt as, ihi, d Ăebbi ay d Bab is, u, deffir waya, ad ilin di talalt is: Jebrayen, Ă»Ă»am n lmumnin, u lmalayek ad fkent afud"
  66,5,"Ma ibra yakwent, Izmer Ăebbi ad as d InĂ»ef s tlawin i kwent yifen, timvuĂąin, tid iumnen, ipĂ©allan, iutuben, iĂąabden, ippuĂ©umen, tid ijeĂŽben tissulya, ne$ tiĂąazriyin"
  66,6,"A wid iumnen! Ăadret iman nnwen akked twacult nnwen, si tmes, is$aĂŽen is d imdanen akked id$a$en! Fellas lmalayek tuohidin, tuqsiĂȘin, ur nepwexxiĂŽ i wayen i sent IumeĂŽ Ăebbi, i ixedmen i sent ipwamĂŽen"
  66,7,"A wid ijehlen, ulay$eĂŽ teste$fĂŽem assa! A ppeppuqeĂźĂźim kan $ef wayen txeddmem"
  66,8,"A wid iumnen! Utubet Ăebbi, ppuba n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ! Ahat Mass nnwen ad awen Ikkes tucmitin nnwen, u a kwen Issekcem ar Loennet, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen. Assen, Ăebbi ur Isdullu Nnbi akked wid iumnen yides. Tafat nnsen teppeddu zdat sen, u yeffus nnsen. Ad qqaĂŽen: \"a Mass nne$! Tim ane$ tafat nne$, SemmeĂȘ ane$; ih, KeĂ§Ă§, Tzemrev i yal cci"
  66,9,"A Nnbi! Nna$ ijehliyen akked ixabiten! IqsiĂȘ $uĂŽsen! Axxam nnsen d Loahennama, d tu$alin tucmip"
  66,10,"Ifka d Ăebbi amedya i wid ijehlen: tameĂźĂźut n NuĂȘ akked tmeĂźĂźut n LuĂź. Llant ger ifassen n sin imdanen, seg wid imaĂąnen n imdanen nne$. ÂŁuĂŒĂŽĂŽent pen. Ur zmiren a tent sselken s wacemma, seg ufus n Ăebbi. Ancad: \"kecmemt ar tmes akked wid ikecmen"
  66,11,"Ifka d Ăebbi amedya i wid iumnen, tameĂźĂźut n FerĂąun, mi tenna: \"a Mass iw! Ebnu yi, $uĂŽeK, taxxamt di Loennet, Sellek iyi si FerĂąun akked igiten is, Sellek iyi si lqum imednas"
  66,12,"U Meryem ult ĂimĂŽan i izazdgen tuzzuft is. Nenfes $uĂŽes si ĂŽĂŽuĂȘ nneÂŁ, tepputebbet $ef wawalen akked tezmamin n Mass is. Neppat seg wid ipĂ©allan"
  67,1,"IĂŽqa Bu tgelda deg ufus iS, u Neppa, Izmer i yal cci"
  67,2,"i Ixelqen tameppant, tameddurt, iwakken a kwen IjeĂŽĂŽeb: anwa degwen ara ixedmen igiten ilhan sennig wiyav. Neppa d Uzmir, IpsemmiĂȘ"
  67,3,"i Ixelqen Ă»a igenwan d idurra. Deg wayen Ixleq UĂȘnin, ur tepwaliv ayen ixuĂ»Ă»en. Ernu sikked ma a pwaliv i$isiyen"
  67,4,"Sinna, ger tiĂź ik berdayen. IĂ©ĂŽi a d iu$al $uĂŽek, iĂȘfa, u inzef"
  67,5,"Ni$ NcebbeĂȘ igenni aqĂŽib s teftilin, NĂŽeooem yisent cwaĂźen, Nhegga yasen aĂąaqeb n tmes"
  67,6,"I wid inekĂŽen Mass nnsen, aĂąaqeb n Loahennama. A tu$alin tucmip"
  67,7,"Mi pwaveggĂŽen $uĂŽes, ad slen la tesraĂąriĂą, u neppat trekkem"
  67,8,"QĂŽib a ppeftutes seg iĂ»iv. Yal tikelt ara iwaveggeĂŽ $uĂŽes urbaĂą, a ten steqsin iĂąssasen is: \"aĂąni ur kwen id iusi ara uneddaĂŽ"
  67,9,"Ad inin: \"ih, iusa ya$ d uneddaĂŽ, nenkeĂŽ u nenna: ur illi ay d Issuder Ăebbi, aql akwen kan di le$wlav meqqwĂŽen"
  67,10,"U nnan: \"lemmer nelli nsell ne$ nfehhem, ur nelli seg wat tmes"
  67,11,QaĂŽĂŽen s ibekkaven nnsen. AsĂȘaq i at tmes
  67,12,"Wanag, i wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen, di tbavnit, ssmaĂȘ akked warraz meqqwĂŽen"
  67,13,"HedĂŽet s sser ne$ Ăąinani, ihi, Neppa IĂ©ĂŽa ayen illan deg idmaren"
  67,14,"Day ur IĂ©ĂŽi ara Win Ixelqen, LaĂźif IppuxebbĂŽen"
  67,15,"Neppa i wen Irran tamurt d tamvuĂąt. ElĂȘut deg ibraĂȘen is, Ă§Ă§et si ĂŽĂŽeĂ©q is. ÂŁuĂŽeS tanekra"
  67,16,"Ma tepputebtem ar, Win Illan deg igenni, ad Irr tamurt a ppertem yiswen? Appan la teppembwiwil"
  67,17,"Ma tepputebtem, ar Win Illan deg igenni, awen d Iazen tabucivant n yid$a$en? D$a, a ppissinem anwa t unabi W"
  67,18,Ni$ nekĂŽen imezwura nnsen. Amek d Zzi$ fellasen
  67,19,"Ahat ur walan ara ifĂŽax, sennig sen, d idurra, afriwen ceĂŽqen, ur cĂŽiqen. Siwa AĂȘnin iten IĂźfen. Neppa, ih, Issikkid yal cci"
  67,20,"Anwa wa ay d aĂąsekĂŽiw nnwen, ara kwen isellken, war AĂȘnin? Ijehliyen atnan kan di le$ĂŽuĂŽ"
  67,21,"Anwa wa ara kwen iĂŽeĂ©qen ma IjmaĂą l$it iS? Maca, vellelen deg u$unfu akked leqbaĂȘa"
  67,22,"Win iteddun, ibra i uqeĂŽĂŽu, day ipwanha sennig win iteddun, irfed aqeĂŽĂŽu, deg ubrid uwqim"
  67,23,"Ini: \"d Neppa ikwen id Ixelqen. Irra yawen timejjin, allen, ulawen. Drus ay tesnemmirem"
  67,24,"Ini: \"d Neppa ikwen isseftin di tmurt, ar $uĂŽeS ara tepwafesrem"
  67,25,"La qqaĂŽen: \"melmi lemĂąahda agi, ma d tidep ay tessawalem"
  67,26,"Ini: \"i IĂ©ĂŽan siwa Ăebbi. Nek d aneddaĂŽ kan ipbegginen"
  67,27,"Mara a t walin iqeĂŽb ed, ad ndellen wudmawen n wid ijehlen. A d inin: \"atan wayen tessuturem"
  67,28,"Ini: \"ma twalam ma In$a ya$ Ăebbi, nek d imeddukwal iw, ne$ ma IĂȘun fella$? Ihi, anwa ara isellken ijehliyen seg uĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan"
  67,29,"Ini: \"Neppa d AĂȘnin, syiS numen, fellaS neppkel. A ppeĂ©ĂŽem anwa i illan di ttelfan n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  67,30,"Ini: \"ma twalam, lemmer ad zzren waman nnwen, w ar awen d iawin aman ippazalen"
  68,1,S wamru akked wayen pjerriden
  68,2,"KeĂ§Ă§, s l$it n Mass ik, ur telliv d aĂŽehbani"
