  68,16,A t Nweccem deg wanzaren
  68,17,"Ih, NjeĂŽĂŽeb iten akken NjeĂŽĂŽeb at leonan, mi gullen, ar di tĂ»ebĂȘit, ad $elten"
  68,18,Ggulen ur ĂȘniten
  68,19,"Tezzi yas tbucivant s$uĂŽ Mass ik, nitni ĂźĂźsen"
